  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 32,
      "chapterTitle": "第一节 数学期望",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "25916006_32_2084-2832",
          "range": "2084-2832",
          "rangeStart": 2084,
          "rangeEnd": 2832,
          "markText": "定义1　设X是离散型的随机变量，其分布律为P（X=xi）=pi，i=1，2，…．如果级数￼绝对收敛，则称\n￼\n为离散型随机变量X的数学期望，也称作期望或均值．",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1750344928,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-06-19 22:55:28",
          "chapterUid": 32,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25916006&chapterUid=32&rangeStart=2084&rangeEnd=2832",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b732490718b72661b755f1?chapterUid=32&rangeStart=2084&rangeEnd=2832"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25916006_6_11885-12072",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "11885-12072",
      "markText": "对立事件一定是互不相容的事件，即但互不相容事件不一定是对立事件；",
      "totalCount": 468,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25916006&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=11885&rangeEnd=12072",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b732490718b72661b755f1?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=11885&rangeEnd=12072"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25916006_8_9686-9742",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "9686-9742",
      "markText": "此外，这个例子的（2）和（3）告诉我们，概率为零的事件未必就是不可能事件，同理，概率为1的事件未必就是必然事件．",
      "totalCount": 216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25916006&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=9686&rangeEnd=9742",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b732490718b72661b755f1?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=9686&rangeEnd=9742"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25916006_15_4769-5176",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "4769-5176",
      "markText": "定义2　设X是一个随机变量，对于任意实数x，称函数 F（x）=P（X≤x），-∞<x<+∞ 为随机变量X的分布函数．",
      "totalCount": 192,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25916006&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=4769&rangeEnd=5176",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b732490718b72661b755f1?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=4769&rangeEnd=5176"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25916006_6_1559-1764",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1559-1764",
      "markText": "随机试验的一切可能结果组成的集合称为样本空间，记为Ω={ω}，其中ω表示试验的每一个可能结果，又称为样本点，即样本空间为全体样本点的集合．",
      "totalCount": 190,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25916006&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1559&rangeEnd=1764",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b732490718b72661b755f1?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1559&rangeEnd=1764"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25916006_9_538-767",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "538-767",
      "markText": "一般地，条件概率是指在某随机事件A发生的条件下，另一随机事件B发生的概率，记为P（B|A），它与P（B）是不同的两类概率．",
      "totalCount": 169,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25916006&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=538&rangeEnd=767",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b732490718b72661b755f1?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=538&rangeEnd=767"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25916006_7_1008-1114",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1008-1114",
      "markText": "概率的统计定义为：随着试验次数n的增大，频率值逐步“稳定”到一个实数，这个实数称为事件A发生的概率．",
      "totalCount": 150,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25916006&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1008&rangeEnd=1114",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b732490718b72661b755f1?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1008&rangeEnd=1114"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25916006_15_2745-3106",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "2745-3106",
      "markText": "在随机试验E中，Ω是相应的样本空间，如果对Ω中的每一个样本点ω，有唯一一个实数X（ω）与它对应，那么就把这个定义域为Ω的单值实值函数X=X（ω）称为（一维）随机变量．",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25916006&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=2745&rangeEnd=3106",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b732490718b72661b755f1?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=2745&rangeEnd=3106"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25916006_6_7821-7965",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "7821-7965",
      "markText": "如果A与B没有相同的样本点，则称事件A与B互不相容（或称为互斥）",
      "totalCount": 136,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25916006&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7821&rangeEnd=7965",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b732490718b72661b755f1?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7821&rangeEnd=7965"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25916006_6_2727-2793",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2727-2793",
      "markText": "样本空间中的元素可以是数，也可以不是数．从样本空间中含有样本点的个数来看，可以是有限个也可以是无限个；可以是可列个也可以是不可列个．",
      "totalCount": 119,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25916006&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2727&rangeEnd=2793",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b732490718b72661b755f1?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2727&rangeEnd=2793"
    },
    {
